  "story": "A deeply comforting keerthanam celebrating God's unchanging love. This traditional hymn has brought solace to Kerala Christians through times of hardship and grief. Sung at prayer meetings and home gatherings, its gentle melody carries the assurance that nothing can separate believers from the unfailing love of God.",
